{
  "stem": "14613.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's Gross-Rosen, that was in Bavaria, in the section of Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there in the camps, the condition-- if you compare this to Auschwitz, you might say, were relatively better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they send us to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of the work was either what they call [SPEAKING GERMAN], which means breaking of stones, or in the forests in Bavaria there, in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The work was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would wake you up at sunrise, or before sunrise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to stay for an hour or two sometimes on the appellplatz, where they were counting you, if everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would send you under guards to the steinbruch, or the forest to chop woods, or to break the stone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was mostly the work that we had to do there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is how we work there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I, in a way, was a little lucky that every now and then I was able to stay in the camp, instead of going out to work, and do some work in the camp because they always needed few people in the camp to take care and to clean up the barracks.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They needed some people to work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that I was able somehow to maneuver, quite often, to stay in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this was a big thing for both of us, for me and for my brother, because when I stayed in the camp, then I was able to organize, which means to steal some food, or some extra piece of clothes, so that when my brother came from work he was able to get a little more food from me.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he had more than just the regular amount that they gave him.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
